high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the sink and look below at the cabinet.
Open the cabinet doors, pick up a gold bowl, shut the doors.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge door, put the bowl down on the third shelf, close the door, open the door, pick up the bowl, close the door.
Look up at the cabinets above the fridge.
Open the cabinet door on the right side, put the bowl down in the cabinet, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To chill a bowl and put it in the cabinet above the fridge.

high_descs: walk to face cabinet under cabinet to the right of the sink
pick up brown cup from cabinet
chill and remove cup from fridge
gaze upwards to cabinet above fridge
Move to the right of the sink, facing the fork and avocado on the counter.
Open the cabinet below the counter and take out the brown bowl.
Turn to the right and head toward the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator and put the brown bowl on the bottom shelf, close the refrigerator, and then open the refrigerator again, take out the brown bowl from the bottom shelf, and close the refrigerator.
Look up at the cabinets above the refrigerator.
Open the right-side cabinet above the refrigerator, put the brown bowl inside the right-side cabinet, and close the right-side cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a brown bowl into the right-side cabinet above a refrigerator.
